The affiliate networks usually just supply a generic links to the sellers page. Most times you want to link to a
specific page on the sellers website. The way to do this is to sign up for the webservice access on LinkShare or
CommissionJunction

This library makes it possible to easily generate an affiliate link for LinkShare or CommissionJunction network by
making calls to the webservice provided by each network


Example CommissionJunction:

CommissionJunctionService cjs = new CommisionJunctionService("your dev key", "pid");
cjs.generateLink("N82E16882021123", "default/url")


Example LinkShare:

LinkShareService lss = new LinkShareService("your dev key", "site key");
lss.generateLink("http://mobile.buy.com/ibuy/Product.aspx?sku=221894403")
